## no-inline-styles

# No Inline Styles

## TRIGGER
ALWAYS ACTIVE - Enforced during code generation and review.

## PURPOSE
Inline styles in JavaScript are a code smell. They mix concerns, make dark mode difficult, and create maintenance nightmares. Always use CSS classes.

## FULL IMPLEMENTATION
When trigger detected, read complete implementation:
```powershell
$content = Get-Content "C:/Users/mike.ullman/OneDrive - Vizio, Inc/Documents/Cline/Rules/full/no-inline-styles.md" -Raw
```

Or use read_file tool:
`full/no-inline-styles.md`

