## pwa-lockdown

# Pwa Lockdown

## TRIGGER
ALWAYS ACTIVE when creating or modifying PWA files.

## PURPOSE
PWAs should feel like native apps - no browser chrome, no zoom, no scroll, no text selection. Lock it down completely.

## FULL IMPLEMENTATION
When trigger detected, read complete implementation:
```powershell
$content = Get-Content "C:/Users/mike.ullman/OneDrive - Vizio, Inc/Documents/Cline/Rules/full/pwa-lockdown.md" -Raw
```

Or use read_file tool:
`full/pwa-lockdown.md`

